<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Bakersfield Real Estate Photography | William Dean Photography – Clean, Fast, Compliant</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Real estate photographer in Bakersfield & Kern County delivering clean, fast, MLS-compliant listing photos, twilight edits, and AI marketing visuals for serious agents." />
  <meta name="keywords" content="William Dean Photography, Bakersfield real estate photographer, Kern County listing photos, MLS compliant photography, twilight edits, AI staging, AI walk-through video, real estate marketing, Bakersfield CA photography, residential listing photos" />
